    "body": "I don't understand the \"onlyListedAttributes\" behavior from reading the documentation, when is it used?\n\nI thought that as soon as you provided a list of attributes inside `attributes.*`, those were the only one displayed.\n\nIf I get it right, you want to pass a list of attributes to then be used as a blacklist to not show them?\n",
